org.cornutum.tcases.openapi.testwriter

Interface TestCaseWriter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RestAssuredTestCaseWriter, TestCaseContentWriter

    public interface TestCaseWriter
    Writes the source code for test cases that execute API requests.
